    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chorizo is cooking, add the <strong>gnocchi</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the gnocchi for 3 min or until it begins to rise to the top of the pot</p><p>Once done, drain the gnocchi, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy cooking water</strong></p>",
